<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf177729-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s10174"><num value="10174">§ 10174.</num><heading> Consideration in siting facilities</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary, in siting Federal research projects, shall give special consideration to proposals from States where a repository is located.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbf17772a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/425/tI/s174">Pub. L. 97–425, title I, § 174</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/100/202/s101/d/tIII/s300">Pub. L. 100–202, § 101(d) [title III, § 300]</ref>, <date date="1987-12-22">Dec. 22, 1987</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/101/1329-104">101 Stat. 1329–104</ref>, 1329–121; <ref href="/us/pl/100/203/tV/s5031">Pub. L. 100–203, title V, § 5031</ref>, <date date="1987-12-22">Dec. 22, 1987</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/101/1330-240">101 Stat. 1330–240</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
